metadata.name: You’re Not Alone - I Hold On by Alice Marinelli
metadata.description:
“Do you ever feel lonely,  
when you’re part of the crowd?  


Does your soul suffer quietly,  
and your heart breaks in half?  


Do you feel like you're standing,  
on the edge of a cliff?  
While slowly losing your breath,  
and everything you believe in?  


You are not alone! It’s important that you know!  
Take my hand and feel the power of togetherness!  


You are not alone! It’s important that you know!  
Take my hand and feel the power of togetherness!”
